==剧情==
通用电气公司负责[[美国东岸|美国东岸]]电视和微波炉业务的副总裁杰克·唐纳吉需要参加一场[[糖尿病|糖尿病]][[慈善|慈善]][[高尔夫|高尔夫]]活动，公司[[CEO|CEO]]唐·盖斯也会参加。杰克希望能给年迈的盖斯留下一个好的印象，增大将来接班的机会，于是他叫上了自己主管的[[喜剧小品|喜剧小品]]《{{lang|en|TGS}}与崔西·乔丹》中的头牌明星崔西·乔丹一起前往。到了聚会现场，崔西很快成为一位受关注的人物，但他也因此感觉自己被带过来这里只是作为一个“有趣的黑人”而感到不满。他指控盖斯没有聘请足够多的[[非裔美国人|黑人]]，有[[种族主义|种族主义]]倾向，这话引起盖斯不快，杰克和崔西也因此没有获得与盖斯一起打高尔夫球的邀请。杰克对崔西感到不满，崔西表示自己就是忍不住，说只有“真心话大冒险”才能解决问题。之后，崔西又一次走到人群注目之下，讲述自己的女儿与粮尿病魔搏斗的事迹，包括盖斯在内的众人都大为感动。盖斯于是邀请杰克、崔西以及崔西“身患糖尿病的女儿”一起去[[马萨葡萄园岛|马萨葡萄园岛]]。杰克对此非常满意，崔西告诉杰克自己压根儿就没有女儿，后者说没关系，[[星期一|星期一]]找演员来试镜就行了。

电视台大楼里，《{{lang|en|TGS}}与崔西·乔丹》首席编剧丽兹·莱蒙和手下众编剧正在讨论有关节目中可以考虑使用的主题。J·D·卢兹提出了自己构想的一个《与流浪汉共舞》（{{lang|en|Dancing with the Hobos}}），但在众人面前受到了丽兹的否决，让他深感难堪。之后，正在和节目养猫人葛丽泰·约翰森交谈的丽兹无意中听到卢兹用[[屄|C开头的词]]辱骂自己。愤怒之下，她告诉节目的[[制片人|制片人]]皮特·霍恩伯格（{{lang|en|Pete Hornberger}}，{{link-en|斯科特·安第斯|Scott Adsit}}饰）和另一位编剧弗兰克·罗斯塔诺（{{lang|en|Frank Rossitano}}，{{link-en|贾达·弗雷德兰德|Judah Friedlander}}饰），表明自己受到了污辱，打算炒卢兹的鱿鱼。弗兰克表示丽兹在手下眼中不是个好上司，丽兹虽然深感意外，但还是决定从今往后在工作上要给同事多留余地。谁料想，她的主动退让却导致众人开始想方设法占便宜，丽兹又气坏了，再一次改变主意，她告诉卢兹，自己听到了他的辱骂，并且警告大家今后谁再用这个“可怕的词”称呼自己就会被[[解雇|解雇]]。

电视台的杂工跟班肯尼斯·帕塞尔（{{lang|en|Kenneth Parcell}}，[[杰克·麦克布瑞尔|杰克·麦克布瑞尔]]饰）对另一位杂工跟班格蕾斯·帕克产生了一种浪漫感觉，但他又担心两人如果交往，将有负电视台的重托和形象，可是他已无法自拔，总觉得对方的行为都是在对自己加以性挑逗。最后，肯尼斯终于鼓起勇气向格蕾斯表白，正当两人就要[[接吻|接吻]]时，有人找肯尼斯做一件工作，他马上就全心全意地投入到工作中，完全忘记了格蕾斯和之前的尴尬。

==制作==
[[File:Tina_Fey_by_David_Shankbone.jpg|thumb]]

《C开头的那个词》由《我为喜剧狂》的主创人、执行制片人兼女主演蒂娜·菲编剧<ref name="sreen" />，这也是她继《[[试播集_(我为喜剧狂)|试播集]]》、《[[后果_(我为喜剧狂)|后果]]》、《[[崔西演柯南|崔西演柯南]]》、《[[头与头发|头与头发]]》、《[[黑领带|黑领带]]》和《[[熬夜_(我为喜剧狂)|熬夜]]》后第7次为这一剧集编剧<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.imdb.com/name/nm0275486/filmoseries#tt0496424 |title=Tina Fey — Filmography by TV series |accessdate=2013-08-07 |publisher=IMDb |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20130325131431/http://www.imdb.com/name/nm0275486/filmoseries#tt0496424 |archivedate=2013-03-25 |deadurl=no }}</ref>。[[导演|导演]]是监督[[制片人|制片人]]亚当·伯恩斯坦，这是他第5次执导《我为喜剧狂》<ref name="sreen">{{cite web |url=http://www.screenrush.co.uk/television/television-813/season-2600/ |title=30 Rock: Episodes |publisher=Screenrush (AlloCiné) |accessdate=2013-07-28 |location=London |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20120730001543/http://www.screenrush.co.uk/television/television-813/season-2600/ |archivedate=2012-07-30 |deadurl=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.imdb.com/name/nm0002835/#Director |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20120827094946/http://www.imdb.com/name/nm0002835/#Director |publisher=IMDb |accessdate=2012-08-27 |archivedate=2012-08-27 |title=Adam Bernstein |deadurl=yes }}</ref>。《C开头的那个词》于2007年2月15日通过全国广播公司在美国首播，是[[喜剧小品|喜剧小品]]《我为喜剧狂》的第14集<ref name="sreen" />。

蒂娜·菲曾于2007年4月接受《[[娱乐周刊|娱乐周刊]]》采访时透露，曾有一位手下的编剧用“[[屄|C开头的那个词]]”骂过自己。“C开头那个词的事件的确发生过。我当时气疯了，反应也很古怪，不停地说，‘你不能这么说！我爸爸妈妈都很爱我！’”<ref name="ew fine">{{cite news|first=Kristen|last=Baldwin|url=http://www.ew.com/ew/article/0,,20033897_2,00.html|title=One Fine Fey|accessdate=2010-03-28|date=2007-04-10|work=Entertainment Weekly|page=2|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20121018010111/http://www.ew.com/ew/article/0%2C%2C20033897_2%2C00.html|archivedate=2012-10-18|dead-url=no}}</ref>而在另一场采访中，当被问起《C开头的那个词》是否是根据真实体验编剧时她回答，“有一点吧，有一点是基于哪个人突然用一个很过火的词骂你，而你一下子也不知道应该怎么反应。”<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.craveonline.com/tv/interviews/155960-tina-fey-gets-the-gold |title=Fey gets the gold |accessdate=2013-08-07 |date=2007-09-16 |publisher=Crave Online |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20120722101810/http://www.craveonline.com/tv/interviews/155960-tina-fey-gets-the-gold |archivedate=2012-07-22 |deadurl=no }}</ref>

曾长期和菲合作的瑞秋·德拉彻<ref>{{cite news |first=Christopher |last=Goodwin |url=http://www.theguardian.com/lifeandstyle/2008/may/11/women.television |title=And funny with it |accessdate=2013-07-31 |date=2008-05-11 |work=The Guardian |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20090225222859/http://www.guardian.co.uk/lifeandstyle/2008/may/11/women.television |archivedate=2009-02-25 |deadurl=no }}</ref>本是扮演简娜·玛隆妮一角的初定人选，并已在节目起初拍摄的试播集中出演了这一角色<ref>{{cite news |first=Justin |last=Ravitz |title=Unemployment’s a Downer for ''SNL''-er Dratch |url=http://nymag.com/news/intelligencer/45792/ |publisher=''New York Magazine'' |date=2008-04-07 |accessdate=2013-07-28 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20121013011052/http://nymag.com/news/intelligencer/45792/ |archivedate=2012-10-13 |deadurl=no }}</ref><ref name="ew fine"/>。但到了2006年8月，执行制片人{{link-en|洛恩·迈克尔斯|Lorne Michaels}}宣布简娜一角将另选演员出演，但德拉彻还是会在之前的多集节目中以不同的身份登场。在最后播出的这集试播集中，她以《女生秀》养猫人葛丽泰·约翰森的身份出镜<ref name="michaelsaboutdratch">{{cite news |first=Michael |last=Schneider |title=Inside Move: Dratch latched to multiple ''Rock'' roles |url=http://variety.com/2006/scene/news/inside-move-dratch-latched-to-multiple-rock-roles-1200342025/ |publisher=''Variety'' |date=2006-08-14 |accessdate=2013-07-28 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20120516190758/http://www.variety.com/index.asp?layout=story&articleID=VR1117948462&cs=1 |archivedate=2012-05-16 |deadurl=no }}</ref>。同月晚些时候，全国广播公司宣布已由简·科拉克斯基取代德拉彻出演简娜一角<ref name="dratchout">{{cite news |url=http://www.zap2it.com/tv/news/zap-janekrakowskijoins30rock,0,1779072.story?coll=zap-tv-headlines |title='Ally' Cat Krakowski Joins '30 Rock' |accessdate=2013-07-28 |date=2006-08-17 |publisher=Zap2it |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20120927030648/http://www.zap2it.com/tv/news/zap-janekrakowskijoins30rock%2C0%2C1779072.story?coll=zap-tv-headlines |archivedate=2012-09-27 |deadurl=yes }}</ref><ref name="dratchout_2">{{cite news |first=Joel |last=Keller |title=Jane Krakowski added to 30 Rock |url=http://www.aoltv.com/2006/08/17/jane-krakowski-added-to-30-rock/ |publisher=AOL's TV Squad |date=2008-08-17 |accessdate=2013-07-28 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20120813214025/http://www.aoltv.com/2006/08/17/jane-krakowski-added-to-30-rock/ |deadurl=no |archivedate=2012-08-13 }}</ref><ref name="dratchout_3">{{cite news |first=Colin |last=Mahan |title=30 Rock adds Jane Krakowski |url=http://www.tv.com/news/30-rock-adds-jane-krakowski--5917/ |publisher=TV.com |date=2006-08-16 |accessdate=2013-07-28 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20080615234403/http://www.tv.com/ally-mcbeal/show/168/story/5917.htmlom_act%3Dconvert%26om_clk%3Dheadlinessh |archivedate=2008-06-15 |deadurl=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite news |first=Rebecca |last=Traister |url=http://www.salon.com/life/broadsheet/2010/04/14/tina_fey_backlash/ |title=The Tina Fey backlash |accessdate=2013-07-31 |date=2010-04-14 |publisher=Salon.com |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20110820213538/http://www.salon.com/life/broadsheet/2010/04/14/tina_fey_backlash |archivedate=2011-08-20 |deadurl=no }}</ref>，在《[[后果_(我为喜剧狂)|后果]]》中，她扮演了一个名叫玛丽娅（{{lang|en|Maria}}）的女佣，丽兹发现她被锁在一艘游艇的衣柜里<ref name="theaftermath">{{cite episode |title=The Aftermath |series=30 Rock |serieslink=我为喜剧狂 |credits=Writer: Tina Fey; Director: Adam Bernstein |network=NBC Universal |station=NBC |airdate=2006-10-18 |season=1 |number=2}}</ref>。在《杰克遇上丹尼斯》里，德拉彻饰演了女演员[[伊丽莎白·泰勒|伊丽莎白·泰勒]]<ref>{{cite episode |title=Jack Meets Dennis |series=30 Rock |credits=Writer: Jack Burditt; Director: Juan J. Campanella |network=NBC Universal |station=NBC |airdate=2006-11-30 |season=1 |number=6}}</ref>。《[[崔西演柯南|崔西演柯南]]》中德拉彻出演的是崔西·乔丹出现幻觉时所看到的一个全身穿上臃肿蓝色服装的人，被称为“小蓝人”<ref name="tracydoesconan">{{cite episode |title=Tracy Does Conan|series=30 Rock |credits=Writer: Tina Fey; Director: Adam Bernstein |network[NBC Universal |station=NBC |airdate=2006-12-07 |season=1 |number=7}}</ref>。在《分手》中，她诠释了帕梅拉·斯缪，是崔西和图弗之间的一组灵敏度训练治疗师成员<ref name="break">{{cite web |url=http://www.imdb.com/title/tt0905647/ |title="30 Rock" The Break-Up (2006) |accessdate=2013-08-01 |publisher=IMDb |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20120802103415/http://www.imdb.com/title/tt0905647/ |archivedate=2012-08-02 |deadurl=no }}</ref>。而到了《幼儿节目》中，德拉彻扮演了一位名叫格丽塔的女子，听说丽兹·莱蒙想怀个孩子后表示自己愿意做她的代孕母亲<ref name="baby show">{{cite episode |title=The Baby Show |series=30 Rock |credits=Writer: Jack Burditt; Director: Michael Engler |network=NBC Universal |station=NBC |airdate=2007-01-04 |season=1 |number=9}}</ref>，而到了《熬夜》里，她饰演的是杰克喝醉后叫来的一个妓女。在《C开头的那个词》中，德拉彻继《试播集》以来再次出演养猫人葛丽泰·约翰森<ref name="plotreference">{{cite episode |title=Pilot |episodelink=试播集 (我为喜剧狂) |series=30 Rock |credits=Writer: Tina Fey; Director: Adam Bernstein |network=NBC Universal |station=NBC |airdate=2006-10-11 |season=1 |number=1}}</ref>。《周六夜现场》还有其他多位演员也参加了《我为喜剧狂》的演出，包括[[弗莱德·阿米森|弗莱德·阿米森]]<ref name="somebody to love">{{cite news |first=Robert |last=Canning |url=http://uk.ign.com/articles/2007/11/16/30-rock-somebody-to-love-review |title=30 Rock: "Somebody to Love" Review |accessdate=2013-07-31 |publisher=IGN |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20121022114115/http://www.ign.com/articles/2007/11/16/30-rock-somebody-to-love-review |archivedate=2012-10-22 |deadurl=no }}</ref>、[[克里斯汀·韦格|克里斯汀·韦格]]<ref name="somebody to love" />、{{link-en|威尔·福特|Will Forte}}<ref>{{cite news |url=http://www.tvguide.com/episode-recaps/30-rock/february-1-2007-5916.aspx |first=Matt |last=Webb Mitovich |title=February 1, 2007: "It Feels Good to Laugh" |accessdate=2013-07-31 |date=2007-02-02 |work=TV Guide |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20121019174231/http://www.tvguide.com/tvshows/30-rock/episode-12-season-1/281135 |archivedate=2012-10-19 |deadurl=yes }}</ref>、{{link-en|莫莉·香侬|Molly Shannon}}<ref>{{cite episode |title=The Fighting Irish |series=30 Rock |credits=Writer: Jack Burditt; Director: Dennie Gordon |network=NBC Universal |station=NBC |airdate=2007-03-08 |season=1 |number=17}}</ref>、{{link-en|霍拉提奥·桑斯|Horatio Sanz}}<ref>{{cite web |url=http://tv.yahoo.com/30-rock/show/anna-howard-shaw-day/episode/229969/castcrew;_ylt=ApAQxiuPKcM.m1DE6hlJnR6xo9EF |title=30 Rock — Anna Howard Shaw Day |accessdate=2011-06-15 |publisher=Yahoo! TV |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20110615061125/http://tv.yahoo.com/30-rock/show/anna-howard-shaw-day/episode/229969/castcrew%3B_ylt%3DApAQxiuPKcM.m1DE6hlJnR6xo9EF |archivedate=2011-06-15 |deadurl=yes }}</ref>、[[杰森·苏戴奇斯|杰森·苏戴奇斯]]、<ref name="sudeikis">{{cite news|first=Whitney|last=Matheson|title=A chat with ... ''30 Rock'' and ''SNL'' star Jason Sudeikis|url=http://content.usatoday.com/communities/popcandy/post/2007/04/159575/1|work=USA Today|date=2007-04-19|accessdate=2013-07-31|archive-date=2013-07-31|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130731101104/http://content.usatoday.com/communities/popcandy/post/2007/04/159575/1|dead-url=no}}</ref>、{{link-en|简·霍克斯|Jan Hooks}}<ref>{{cite news |first=Alan |last=Sepinwall |url=http://www.nj.com/entertainment/tv/index.ssf/2010/02/30_rock_verna_jan_hooks_guest-.html |title=30 Rock, 'Verna': Jan Hooks guest-stars |accessdate=2013-08-02 |date=2010-02-04 |work=The Star-Ledger |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20121010221813/http://www.nj.com/entertainment/tv/index.ssf/2010/02/30_rock_verna_jan_hooks_guest-.html |archivedate=2012-10-10 |deadurl=no }}</ref>、[[克里斯·帕内尔|克里斯·帕内尔]]<ref>{{cite web |url=http://tv.yahoo.com/30-rock/show/the-baby-show/episode/115158/castcrew;_ylt=AvuPPAZBbLa7hQG9q4bBRVivo9EF |title=30 Rock — The Baby Show |accessdate=2010-04-21 |publisher=Yahoo! TV |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20110615060804/http://tv.yahoo.com/30-rock/show/the-baby-show/episode/115158/castcrew%3B_ylt%3DAvuPPAZBbLa7hQG9q4bBRVivo9EF |archivedate=2011-06-15 |deadurl=yes }}</ref><ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.imdb.com/title/tt0931394/ |title=30 Rock The Baby Show (TV Episode 2007) |publisher=IMDb |accessdate=2013-08-02 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20110909071159/http://www.imdb.com/title/tt0931394/ |archivedate=2011-09-09 |deadurl=no }}</ref><ref name="baby show" /><ref name="parnell">{{cite news |first=Annie |last=Barrett |authorlink= |coauthors= |title=What ''SNL'' alums besides Chris Parnell should guest on ''30 Rock''? |url=http://popwatch.ew.com/2006/12/07/what_snl_alums_/ |work= |publisher=''Entertainment Weekly'' |date=2006-12-07 |accessdate=2013-08-01 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20130608163606/http://popwatch.ew.com/2006/12/07/what_snl_alums_/ |archivedate=2013-06-08 |deadurl=no }}</ref>等。菲和崔西·摩根都曾是《周六夜现场》的主要演员<ref>{{cite news |url=http://uk.ign.com/articles/2006/10/18/ign-interview-30-rocks-tracy-morgan |title=IGN Interview: 30 Rock's Tracy Morgan |accessdate=2010-03-27 |last=Fickett |first=Travis |date=2006-10-17 |publisher=IGN |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20130728020822/http://www.ign.com/articles/2006/10/18/ign-interview-30-rocks-tracy-morgan |archivedate=2013-07-28 |deadurl=no }}</ref><ref name="tinafey_yahoo">{{cite web|url=http://tv.yahoo.com/person/tina-fey/biography.html|title=Tina Fey Biography|accessdate=2013-08-01|last=|first=|coauthors=|date=|work=|publisher=''Yahoo!''|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20130801081437/http://tv.yahoo.com/person/tina-fey/biography.html|archivedate=2013-08-01}}</ref>。亚历克·鲍德温也曾16次担任《周六夜现场》主持人，创下了该节目的最高纪录<ref name="alec_snl">{{cite episode |title=Alec Baldwin/Christina Aguilera |episodelink= |series=Saturday Night Live |serieslink=周六夜现场 |credits= |network=NBC Universal |station=NBC |airdate=2006-11-11 |season=32 |seriesno= |number=5 |minutes= }}</ref>。此外，《C开头的那个词》还是雷普·汤恩首次在《我为喜剧狂》亮相，他扮演的是通用电气首席执行官唐·盖斯<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.imdb.com/name/nm0001800/filmoseries#tt0496424|title=Rip Torn — Filmography by TV series|accessdate=2013-08-07|publisher=IMDb|archive-date=2013-08-07|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130807050704/http://www.imdb.com/name/nm0001800/filmoseries#tt0496424|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

==反响==
根据尼尔森收视率调查的数据，《C开头的那个词》在美国首播时有约500万户家庭观看，在18-49岁人群中获得的收视率为2.5 / 6。这个数字意味着首播时全美所有这一年龄段人群中有2.5%看了这集节目，而当时有看电视的这个年龄段观众群里则有6%选择收看《C开头的那个词》<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.thefutoncritic.com/news.aspx?id=20070221nbc02|title=NBC Ratings Results For The Week Of Feb. 12-18|accessdate=2013-08-07|publisher=The Futon Critic|archive-date=2012-09-09|archive-url=https://www.webcitation.org/6AXtZQTHH?url=http://www.thefutoncritic.com/news.aspx?id=20070221nbc02|dead-url=no}}</ref>。与上一集《熬夜》首播时520万户家庭观看的成绩相比有所下降<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.thefutoncritic.com/news.aspx?date=02/13/07&id=20070213nbc02|title=NBC Ratings Results For The Week Of Feb. 5-11 -- The #1 New Show Of The Season In 18-49, 'Heroes,' Is The Top-Rated Program On Television Monday And The Top-Rated New Series Of The Week In Adults 18-49, 18-34 And 25-54|accessdate=2013-08-07|date=2007-02-13|publisher=The Futon Critic|archive-date=2013-02-15|archive-url=https://www.webcitation.org/6ES3eXUpS?url=http://www.thefutoncritic.com/news.aspx?date=02%2F13%2F07|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

[[IGN|IGN]]网站的罗伯特·坎宁（{{lang|en|Robert Canning}}）写道，“像《C开头的那个词》这样的一集虽说剧情上有些简单短小，但仍然有足够值得一提的爆笑桥段……总而言之，出众的剧本抵消了略显不足的部分，让这成为又一集充满欢笑的《我为喜剧狂》。”坎宁认为杰克·唐纳吉和崔西·乔丹在性格上完全是地球的两极，这一集中把这两个人物放在一起，有着很让人满意的效果。他还觉得丽兹的故事线索虽然有一些好笑的地方，但与这个角色以往所塑造的形象有些不符。坎宁最终给予这一集的评分为7.8（最高为10）<ref>{{cite news |first=Robert |last=Canning |url=http://www.ign.com/articles/2007/02/16/30-rock-the-c-word-review |title=30 Rock: "The 'C' Word" Review |accessdate=2013-08-07 |date=2007-02-16 |publisher=IGN TV |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20120606141920/http://tv.ign.com/articles/765/765379p1.html |archivedate=2012-06-06 |deadurl=no }}</ref>。[[美国在线|美国在线]]电视小队的朱丽亚·沃德（{{lang|en|Julia Ward}}）认为把亚历克·鲍德温和雷普·汤恩凑到一块的作法是“天才般的一步”。她还称赞蒂娜·菲又给出了优异的表现，“继续描绘出一位努力工作女生的真实形象”。沃德也很喜欢崔西一角在剧中的演说，称其“价值无法估量”，并且很高兴这个角色有了“充足的出场时间……这对节目的步调是一个很好的调整”<ref>{{cite news |first=Julia |last=Ward |url=http://www.aoltv.com/2007/02/16/30-rock-the-c-word/ |title=30 Rock: The "C" Word |accessdate=2013-08-07 |date=2007-02-16 |publisher=TV Squad |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20120531065332/http://www.aoltv.com/2007/02/16/30-rock-the-c-word/ |archivedate=2012-05-31 |deadurl=no }}</ref>。[[电视指南_(美国杂志)|电视指南]]的马特·米托维奇（{{lang|en|Matt Mitovich}}）对这一集所有的故事线索都感到满意，并且特别喜欢杰克和崔西的部分。米托维奇在对节目的总结中认为丽兹一角的故事线索可以做得更好，不过他仍然称赞这个故事中“包含着适当的信息：作为一位女性首席编剧，她的标准与通常的理解有所不同。此外，她的故事还让我们回想起那些她……不是个乖乖女的时刻”<ref>{{cite news |first=Matt |last=Mitovich |url=http://www.tvguide.com/tvshows/30-rock/episode-14-season-1/281135 |title=February 15, 2007: "When You Said Hello, You Had Me" |accessdate=2013-08-07 |date=2007-02-15 |work=TV Guide |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20121112093312/http://www.tvguide.com/tvshows/30-rock/episode-14-season-1/281135 |archivedate=2012-11-12 |deadurl=no }}</ref>。

